Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和酷一行人同行的菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.79,0:02:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在ChaosChoir的命令下\N为离间酷和蕾而接近他们的间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的话就能成为煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她多年的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.84,0:02:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知不觉间菲萝真的喜欢上了酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.69,0:02:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而蕾也对心中所萌发的前所未有的感觉不知所措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.20,0:02:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十九唱 碎石的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.51,0:03:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 以及其他人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 把你吵醒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续两天星夜赶路实在是撑不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以正在做住宿的准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这车子也是用了二十年的半淘汰品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也很吃不消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是搭好了 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了我们的努力 对吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一切都是菲萝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等 沾在脸上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我过去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.78,0:04:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一个人待一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我想单独待着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和酷在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感觉很热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得啊 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然也下厨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶儿也动动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可能在约会什么的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 怎么做呢 菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步骤就请问龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个 是说酷的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动了真情可就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初可能是为了别的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别隐瞒了 别隐瞒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初只是Fan和偶像的关系就很心满意足了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是说那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是酷很单纯或者该说是很纯真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.42,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时也很想好好疼爱他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇雅说的是另一种意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛がる有两种意思，一是疼爱，二是严加管教{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 以后再也不说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷和蕾又没有结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱是自由的 尽情去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吧 说这么不负责任的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不要留下遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你已跟蕾一样是我们的同伴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.97,0:06:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想越不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不顾别人的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.94,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去打水 陪我一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.22,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次同契的时候我自出生以来第一次感觉到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步的和谐感什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次的时候我也感觉非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 就像飞机机翼一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.79,0:07:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.90,0:07:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴啊 这就是默契吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷觉得谁更好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个 怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么问的话我也不知该怎么答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况我觉得菲萝和蕾各有各的优点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是体贴啊 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.04,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 我只是实话实说而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你这么说我精神好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一起旅行的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会说出那些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热热的 不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是说不上话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行啊 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃...吃太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果完全没机会和蕾说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会讨厌我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战好像很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.45,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个同契者和蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯的心正在疏远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.59,0:09:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 照这样子下去完成任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功之后你就能成为煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.51,0:09:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时就能和你那块破石头说再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蕾她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太接近煌珠乐园了变得更容易疲劳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.74,0:09:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概正睡得香吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是累了正睡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.25,0:10:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这里我能做个普通的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然萌发了不必要的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了一个好点子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 可以让我来做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊芙大人的状态也不容乐观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态紧急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩闹也要适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用那女孩一举将蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯从酷德身边分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐弯抹角的 这可不是游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败的话就抛弃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是有缺陷的破石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.07,0:11:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悬架以及其它一些部件都好像出现了松动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也许得花上一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.09,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去找点食物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这是技术活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.66,0:11:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这也不像是小姐干的活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.79,0:11:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们两人出去一会儿行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.23,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到离这不远有处清澈的泉水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和蕾加深友谊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.27,0:11:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借你泳衣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.42,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过反正也没人看到 裸体也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.45,0:11:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裸 裸体...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸红什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说在幻想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇雅 我们也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护那两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好清澈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡你们也来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣还有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.68,0:12:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要看守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说你也不会游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且菲萝的泳装...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胸部...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想其实不用躲起来换衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过下意识地就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 最近状态怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟往常一样精神满满的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.86,0:13:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神满满的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 快来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.13,0:13:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有话要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么守护翼会变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又是个本质问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由自主地就在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝很开朗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚懂事的年龄就被改造成拟煌珠应该是很悲惨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 一下子 我可不会游泳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.91,0:14:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很浅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.34,0:14:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝的核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽会说笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不像蕾那样的完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢那颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.83,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾喜欢酷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是...那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是恋人了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样算是恋人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个比如说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做过接吻什么之类的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是恋人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我也非常喜欢酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.74,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我成为他的恋人你没意见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.19,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没意见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果酷没意见的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你别埋怨我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷可能也觉得还是菲萝好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的 这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 好兆头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么弄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃的话怎么都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃走了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 多吃点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.92,0:16:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在我们这么欢笑期间不知敌人会什么时候来袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.35,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心 那个时候我和酷会把他们打得落花流水的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.26,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和菲萝合作一下子就能搞定 没什么好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.10,0:17:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 快点吃完继续做剩下的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.12,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能过来一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.88,0:17:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 稍微失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 小菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿京娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.50,0:17:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去和酷德结婚的话我会祝福你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.76,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯的力量让你成为煌珠之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你举行一个盛大的结婚典礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.14,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你送去一匹刺客要好好利用加深和酷的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 和酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 为了这个而苦恼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么突然说讨厌我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和蕾说话才想和她独处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊 龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很认真地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.43,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是酷 你之前不是说过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾要是多少吃点醋就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.35,0:18:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是说过 那又怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾的那种态度怎么想都是在吃醋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.46,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概对蕾来说也是潜意识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么做才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不愿和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是 大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.27,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.05,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.55,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 看到蕾了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.40,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里了啊 我找了半天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.92,0:19:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 快躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是从哪儿冒出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 我们一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.52,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.47,0:19:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天来的时候觉得很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真的很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想说同样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.63,0:20:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.83,0:20:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.15,0:20:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢 不知为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.49,0:21:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲萝 菲萝是破石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.68,0:22:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的唆使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.32,0:22:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的劝戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.00,0:22:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动摇的心中能得出答案吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.39,0:22:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 拟煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.21,0:23:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十唱 拟煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.31,0:23:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而带给少女的又是...
